snippet.title: Void Arena  --  Early Alpha Teaser Trailer v1.1 [UE4, Gameplay Abilities System]
snippet.description:
https://voidarenagame.com/

VOID: ARENA is a First Person, Action/Adventure RPG being developed in Unreal Engine with a focus on fast paced combat, immersive storytelling, and customization allowing players to blaze their own trails.

For info on how to join our public alpha visit our Discord Channel:
https://discord.gg/p3QmXNQ
Wish list on STEAM: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1280210/VOID_Arena/
